ur exterior parts range can expand your BODYPARTS category with competitive pricing.\n\nWould you be interested in reviewing our catalog?\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]','Premium body, engine Wholesale Supply - Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd.','Dear sales,\n\nWe are writing to introduce Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd., a leading China-based automotive parts manufacturer and exporter. With years of experience in distributing, we specialize in auto body parts including bumpers, grilles, panels, doors, fenders, hoods, and more.\n\nWe understand that Aik-E Auto Parts is engaged in OEM and aftermarket parts: engine parts, body parts, chassis parts, electrical parts, air conditioning parts, lubricants. As a reliable partner, we can offer competitive wholesale prices and flexible MOQs for your wholesale distribution.\n\nOur advantages include:\n- Competitive pricing with direct factory supply\n- High-quality products meeting international standards\n- Flexible MOQ and fast delivery\n- wholesale distribution\n\nPlease visit our website https://www.carparts-land.com/ to explore our full product catalog.\n\nWe would be delighted to discuss how we can support your business needs. Could you kindly share your current sourcing requirements or any specific products you are interested in?\n\nLooking forward to your reply.\n\nBest regards,\nFoshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd.\nhttps://www.carparts-land.com/',85,'A',NULL,1,1,0,'100-500',0,'Manual',NULL,NULL,'New',0,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-26 15:45:31','2026-06-26 18:34:36',NULL,'sales',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
