ality, IATF 16949 certified\n• Custom molding (30-45 days)\n• MOQ: 50 sets per model\n• 30-40% cost reduction vs. OEM\n• Export-standard packaging\n\nGiven your strong export business through Siam Bliss Inter Group, we can be a reliable supplementary supplier.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]','Premium ac Wholesale Supply - Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd.','Dear 网站询盘系统,\n\nWe are writing to introduce Foshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd., a leading China-based automotive parts manufacturer and exporter. With years of experience in distributing, we specialize in auto air-conditioning parts including compressors, condensers, evaporators, and blower motors.\n\nWe understand that ThailandAutopart.com (Thai Mitsu/Universal/Siam Bliss) is engaged in auto parts and accessories. As a reliable partner, we can offer competitive wholesale prices and flexible MOQs for your wholesale distribution.\n\nOur advantages include:\n- Competitive pricing with direct factory supply\n- High-quality products meeting international standards\n- Flexible MOQ and fast delivery\n- wholesale distribution\n\nPlease visit our website https://www.carparts-land.com/ to explore our full product catalog.\n\nWe would be delighted to discuss how we can support your business needs. Could you kindly share your current sourcing requirements or any specific products you are interested in?\n\nLooking forward to your reply.\n\nBest regards,\nFoshan Dinghesheng Auto Parts Co., Ltd.\nhttps://www.carparts-land.com/',91,'A',NULL,1,0,0,'500+',0,'Manual',NULL,NULL,'New',0,NULL,NULL,'2026-06-26 15:45:31','2026-06-26 18:28:48',NULL,'网站询盘系统',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
